title: Volleyball Roundup: Ridgewood advances
text:
CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Ridgewood 3, Edison 0 
Host Ridgewood defeated Edison 25-13, 25-17, 25-15 Saturday in a Division II district quarterfinal. The third-seeded Generals (21-3) will meet top-seeded Buckeye Trail at 6 p.m. Wednesday in a district semifinal. 
Allie Dobson had 11 kills, five blocks and two digs for Ridgewood; Laura Crawford had seven kills, three blocks, three digs and one ace; Sydney Zinkon had four aces, 10 assists and three digs; Morgan McDorman had six digs and one ace; Erinn Buchanan had five blocks and three kills; Eliza Haynes had 15 assists, six digs and two kills; and Autumn Brown had three kills and two blocks.
